{"tid":726352,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"（露營jj)有冇咩睡袋好推介","createTime":"2018-07-02T10:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T15:31:49.000Z","uid":58954,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4fbd86d4e3910d88dd594271813c3c95407befb8","tid":726352,"uid":58954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:16:00.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次露營想搵個睡袋 頂到5度左右就ok<br />\n睇過之前巴打啲post話nature hike可以粗玩 但係入面都有好多揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔知邊款好<br />\n有冇巴打可以share下邊款睡袋好用或者share下自己用緊咩睡袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBudget 希望可以壓到500$內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0ec119aa2ec9b230359a0b0842cafe2ba9976c9","tid":726352,"uid":58954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T10:58:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73d753a96d6d90bd8f8d61abc2a689291d62f637","tid":726352,"uid":22928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"睡袋主要分夾棉同羽絨，夾棉平好多，但收埋好大舊同重D，羽絨貴好多，但收埋細同輕好多，睇你想玩一兩次定長玩？"},{"pid":"ea308c844a256d141056be5e273d7d84000ff576","tid":726352,"uid":58954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73d753a96d6d90bd8f8d61abc2a689291d62f637","tid":726352,"uid":22928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:01:44.000Z","msg":"睡袋主要分夾棉同羽絨，夾棉平好多，但收埋好大舊同重D，羽絨貴好多，但收埋細同輕好多，睇你想玩一兩次定長玩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:30:21.000Z","msg":"我會想每年秋冬都用幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我都想要個輕啲 或者巴打覺得一個睡袋可接受範圍係幾重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b7ed811fa15786835aedaa9f2725cdf111562c","tid":726352,"uid":22928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:53:46.